    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Brushes with flat wooden handles of varying length mounted with very stiff bristles in a long, narrow formation, used to spread paste on the back of wallpaper and also to press the pasted paper onto the wall.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
